  "title": "QAQC Engineer",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Assist in the implementation of Project Quality Plan;</li>\n  <li>Assist in preparation of weekly &amp; monthly reports on QAQC matters;</li>\n  <li>Lead the QA/QC team and train the site team on Structural and Architectural trades;</li>\n  <li>Conduct inspections to in-progress / completed works and ensure Works are in accordance to project specification and approved construction drawings;</li>\n  <li>Raise report of any non-conformances and carry out root cause analysis;</li>\n  <li>Assess site operations and procedures daily and recommend improvement actions.</li>\n  <li>Adhere to safety practices in the workplace.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>REQUIREMENT:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Civil Engineering or construction related field</li>\n  <li>At least 3 years of building and/or civil engineering experience.</li>\n  <li>Knowledge in Structural and Architectural works</li>\n  <li>Able to work in Changi East area</li>\n</ul>",
